6.3. The operator may allow third parties, including its authorized service providers, advertising companies and advertising networks to display advertisements in the application. These companies may use tracking technologies, such as "cookies", to collect information about users who view or interact with their advertisements. The use that these companies make of these technologies is subject to their own privacy policies and not the operator's privacy policy.
